        | #[strong Explaining Black Box with visual exploration of Latent Space]
        br
        | #[em Bodria Francesco, Rinzivillo Salvatore, Fadda Daniele, Guidotti Riccardo, Fosca Giannotti, Pedreschi Dino] (2022) - EUROVIS 2022
        #collapse-six.collapse(aria-labelledby='heading-six' data-parent='#accordion-six')
